docs.lead_paragraph: GENEVA, May 23. -- The bulletin of statistics of the League of Nations for May, giving the world's March trade figures in the old gold dollar shows that both imports and exports rose as compared with the previous month, but were less than for March, 1933.

docs.lead_paragraph: OSAKA, May 7. -- The first Japanese company to manufacture automobile parts was started recently at Koyashu, near Yokohama. Should this enterprise be successful, Japan will have the only industry that she has been almost entirely without until the present time.

headline.main: AUTO PARTS PLANT CAPS JAPAN'S BOOM; Recently-Opened Factory at Koyashu Viewed as Symbol of Trade Revival.

docs.snippet: The dollar was strong last week, measured by the quotation for the French franc. It reached a premium of .5 cents, on Saturday, on a rally from parity made on Tuesday. The closing value of .4 cents, showed a gain of .1 cent over the previous week....
docs.lead_paragraph: The dollar was strong last week, measured by the quotation for the French franc. It reached a premium of .5 cents, on Saturday, on a rally from parity made on Tuesday. The closing value of .4 cents, showed a gain of .1 cent over the previous week. Trading was moderately active. The range a year ago was 86.58@ 83.81 cents.
